Imports System Imports System.IO Imports System.Net
Public Class Snippet
Public Shared Function GetFTPDirectory(ByVal user As System.String, ByVal passwort As System.String, ByVal server As System.String, ByVal Dateiname As System.String, ByVal passive As System.Boolean) As System.String Dim FtpFileUri = New Uri(server + Dateiname) Dim DirectoryReq As FtpWebRequest = FtpWebRequest.Create(FtpFileUri) DirectoryReq.Method = WebRequestMethods.Ftp.ListDirectory DirectoryReq.UsePassive = passive DirectoryReq.KeepAlive = False DirectoryReq.Credentials = New NetworkCredential(user, passwort) Dim sw As New StringWriter() Dim dirresponse As FtpWebResponse Try dirresponse = DirectoryReq.GetResponse Catch ex as Exception Return "Err: " + ex.Message End Try Dim responsestream As Stream = dirresponse.GetResponseStream 'Convert the response to a string Dim ch As Integer
Dim returnstr As String = "" While InlineAssignHelper(ch, responsestream.ReadByte()) <> -1 returnstr = returnstr & Convert.ToChar(ch) End While 'clean up responsestream.Close() dirresponse.Close()
Return returnstr
End Function
Private Shared Function InlineAssignHelper(Of T)(ByRef target As T, ByVal value As T) As T target = value Return value End Function
End Class

Imports System.Net Imports System
Public Class Snippet
Public Shared Function FTPDeleteFile(ByVal Benutzer As System.String, ByVal Passwort As System.String, ByVal Server As System.String, ByVal Dateiname As System.String, ByVal passive As System.Boolean) As System.String Dim returnstring As String = "ERR: Fehler bei Verbindung" Dim FtpFileUri = New Uri(Server + Dateiname) Dim DeleteReq As FtpWebRequest = FtpWebRequest.Create(FtpFileUri) DeleteReq.Method = WebRequestMethods.Ftp.DeleteFile DeleteReq.UsePassive = passive DeleteReq.KeepAlive = False DeleteReq.Credentials = New NetworkCredential(Benutzer, Passwort) returnstring = "OK" Try Dim delresponse As FtpWebResponse = DeleteReq.GetResponse returnstring = delresponse.StatusDescription Catch ex As Exception returnstring = "ERR: " + ex.Message End Try Return returnstring
End Function
End Class
